## Arquivos cr\u00edticos j\u00e1 criados
- `prisma/schema.prisma` + migra\u00e7\u00e3o
- `src/lib/db/prisma.ts`
- `src/lib/cloudinary/{client.ts, parsePublicId.ts}`
- `src/lib/groq/client.ts` (generateCaption + generateCaptions)
- `src/lib/huggingface/client.ts` (callHFSpace REAL)
- `src/lib/schemas/{config.ts, compose.ts, caption.ts}`
- `src/lib/hooks/use-tryon.ts`
- `src/lib/utils.ts`
- `src/components/{ui,upload,config,generation,compose,caption}/*` (15+ componentes)
- `src/app/{api,config,generate,compose,caption}/` (5 API routes + 5 p\u00e1ginas)
- `src/app/{error.tsx, global-error.tsx, not-found.tsx}` (error boundaries + 404)
- `playwright.config.ts` (mobile-first)
- `tests/e2e/{navigation.spec.ts, api.spec.ts}` (19 testes)
- `docs/E2E-CHECKLIST.md` (checklist detalhado pra Iago)

## Vari\u00e1veis de ambiente
- `DATABASE_URL` (Neon)
- `CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME`, `CLOUDINARY_API_KEY`, `CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET`
- `GROQ_API_KEY`, `GROQ_MODEL=qwen/qwen3-32b`
- `HF_TOKEN` (opcional)
- `VTON_PROVIDER=hf`

## Pend\u00eancias conhecidas
- **Cerebras/OpenRouter fallback** (placeholder no `lib/groq/client.ts`)
- **FASHN provider** n\u00e3o implementado
- **LGPD banner SSR flicker** (mitiga\u00e7\u00e3o futura)
- **Valida\u00e7\u00e3o runtime** das 5 telas com imagem real \u2014 PENDENTE (Iago precisa testar no device de origem com `.env.local`)
- **`callHFSpace()`** implementado mas n\u00e3o testado com imagem real

